Also it says I can not play it unless I allow it to manage my Google play games data. (I had a look it is quite not clear what kind of data it collects, I only agreed that it sees and manages only this games data in my Google play games aka Google drive ) anyway am sure other people will find it enjoyable.

This game is too cute and the music is addictive. I think I could dance on this for a long time. My only issue is the few seconds it takes to get back to dancing after a round. It's simply quite awesome!

The game could be fun if they actually let you play it for a reasonable amount of time. Your character gets to dance for 15-20 seconds, then the round is over. Back to the menu, unlock some stuff. Dance for 15 seconds. Back to the menu. Collect 5 candies, over in 20 seconds. It's not fun when 90% of the game is spent in the menus. I want to be to play for several minutes before the round ends, not just a few seconds.

It is full of issues. Freezes on start up, always says I'm going to fast, when I'm not. Doesn't reward me for completed levels. I don't get how anyone can play this game with these issues. I have installed and uninstalled on various devices, and it's always the same issue.
